  <h1 class="display-3  text-center mb-5 text-dark fw-bold animated-title">Find Your Nanny</h1>
  <p class="text-center text-muted mb-4">
    Browse through our nannies and find the perfect match for your family ðŸ‘©.</p>

  <div class="row">
